      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Collector Health\nLocal collector, export, privacy poison, Azure, Grafana, schema, and dashboard version status. Uses AgentOps V2 custom tables when present and falls back to existing Copilot OpenTelemetry in Application Insights. If every panel is empty, run `agentops collector smoke --privacy strict --poison --json`; for local demos run `agentops demo generate --runs 50 --with-failures --with-privacy-drops --json`."
